---
---
<section id="hero" class="relative overflow-hidden pt-20 pb-28 px-4 min-h-[85vh] flex items-center">
  <!-- Hero-specific glow orb -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/15 via-neon-purple/10 to-transparent blur-[100px] pointer-events-none animate-glow-pulse" />

  <!-- Tron Grid Floor -->
  <div class="hero-grid" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="hero-grid-inner" />
  </div>
  <div class="hero-horizon" aria-hidden="true" />

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-7 max-w-3xl">
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 w-fit mx-auto backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
            <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-primary opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-primary"></span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Full Business Growth</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-white text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
          No construimos software.
          <span class="text-gradient"> Construimos crecimiento.</span>
        </h1>

        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-primary/90 font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl">
          Full Business Growth: tecnología + estrategia + automatización en un solo equipo.
        </p>

        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-slate-400 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Conectamos tu operación, tus ventas y tu tecnología para que cada pieza de tu negocio empuje en la misma dirección.
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
          <a
            href="#contacto"
            class="group relative bg-primary text-background-dark px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-2 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(19,200,236,0.3)] hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(19,200,236,0.5)] hover:scale-[1.02]"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-0.5">calendar_today</span>
            Agendar reunión
          </a>
          <a
            href="#full-business-growth"
            class="group border border-slate-600 text-slate-300 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/5 hover:border-primary/40 transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5">arrow_forward</span>
            ¿Qué es Full Business Growth?
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-3 text-slate-500 text-sm tracking-wide">Sin compromiso · 30 min · 100% gratis</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-grid {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: -20%;
    right: -20%;
    height: 55%;
    perspective: 350px;
    overflow: hidden;
    pointer-events: none;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 40%, transparent 70%);
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.2) 40%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .hero-grid-inner {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    transform: rotateX(60deg);
    transform-origin: center top;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    animation: grid-scroll 4s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes grid-scroll {
    0%   { background-position: 0 0; }
    100% { background-position: 0 60px; }
  }

  .hero-horizon {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 42%;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 5%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3) 30%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.25) 50%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3) 70%, transparent 95%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2), 0 0 60px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1);
    animation: horizon-pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @keyframes horizon-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; }
    50%      { opacity: 1; }
  }
</style>
